==Description==
The '''Never Melt Ice''' is a type of [[Held Items|Held Item]] that can only be equipped to [[File:Ice_Type_icon.png|30px]]Ice type Pokémon.

==Details==
Raises the attack of the Pokémon holding the Item by 10%.

